*throws tododeku royalty au at you and runs*

So here are the first drawings of my royalty au! I had a lot of fun with coloring these, I really think that I’m getting the hang of colors!

All the other characters DO have parts, and I’ll probably post them later! For the time being, Todoroki and Midoriya are the princes of their respective kingdoms who keep running into each other at the most random places. they’re both smitten, pining, and clueless as everyone else who exists tries to wingman.

Also mama Inko is a queen FIGHT ME

title: Sweet Treats
description:
by Rainbow__Dinosaur

The first time he comes home to find Katsuki eating a sugary sweet donut, it turned Izuku on so much.

Katsuki’s eyes were closed, cheeks slightly flushed, and he had a smile on his face that was so pure it almost reminded him of when they were kids. And the noises he was making? Damn, he sounded like he was really enjoying himself.

The soft moans, and whines that came out of him when he popped a piece of that donut into his mouth, was so. Fucking. Hot.
